name: Experiment Or Die #173
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets and ever expanding content creation. Todays piece is VERY BASIC... If you are here and you are working hard every day, making genuine connections, taking the time to get to know other people and artists and are supportive by whatever means you are able, there is no where for you to go but TO THE MOON! Be real, be honest and be active and it could change your life. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
